 - 採桑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Lang-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-gia-T%E1%BB%91ng-th%E1%BB%8B/author-LvQjrZ3Vk_66BuQTmne2Jg">Lang đại gia Tống thị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Lan-Anh-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Hu%E1%BB%87-Anh/T%C3%B4-%C4%91%C3%A0i-tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-07/poem-pvkTGe67zSoCm74IpeWnGg">Tô đài trúc chi từ kỳ 07 - 蘇台竹枝詞其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Lan-Anh-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Hu%E1%BB%87-Anh/author--wNQkHt_M9ki486cqk9mrA">Tiết Lan Anh, Tiết Huệ Anh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%81u-Th%C3%A1i/V%C5%A9-trung-%E1%BB%A9c-phu-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem--2vpooyFyZxt2IE9vw5GUw">Vũ trung ức phu kỳ 2 - 雨中憶夫其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%81u-Th%C3%A1i/author-kneU-kTQ3K5Go-cxqC9RGA">Triều Thái</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
